yle></th></tr></tbody></table>
<p>The <a href="/RSI" class="mw-redirect" title="RSI">RSI</a> <b>Orion</b> is the premiere spatial mining platform, fully compatible with all <a href="/index.php?title=Mark_IV_Remote_Mining_Device&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Mark IV Remote Mining Device (page does not exist)">Mark IV Remote Mining Devices</a>, and featuring an onboard refinery and a system of saddlebag-class storage units. The Orion's features include high-grade turret-mounted tractor beam arrays, plenty of mineral storage.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
