<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Pledge_Description">Pledge Description</span></h2>
<blockquote><p>Roberts Space Industries’ goal has always been to make the stars available to individual Citizens. Now, with the RSI Orion mining platform, RSI is letting individuals take over a process formerly controlled by mega-corporations.</p></blockquote>
